load-media - Media Loader

USAGE:
    load-media <media-dir>

DESCRIPTION:
    Load media from a source directory. Mounts the media if needed,
    prepares target, and copies media files.

ARGUMENTS:
    media-dir
        Media source directory (required)

NOTE:
    Requires root privileges.

EXAMPLES:
    load-media /media/usb
    load-media /mnt/dvd
